You are here: Easily Add Grantmaking Permission Sets to Permission Set Groups

To give more permissions to or remove permissions from users, create custom permission sets. Then, include your custom permission sets in a permission set group with the Grantmaking permission. This approach ensures users always have the latest default permissions and is an alternative to cloning permission sets.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer editions where Grantmaking is enabled.
title: Easily Add Grantmaking Permission Sets
